Cluster Sizing

bootstrap
/ default AMI setting (minimum 100G)
/boot default AMI setting
/home default AMI setting
/var default AMI setting (minimum 200G)
/var/log default AMI setting (minimum 20G)
/tmp default AMI setting (minimum 10G)
/opt (optional) default AMI setting (minimum 20G)
swap default AMI setting

